_refine.details                                  
;Molecular replacement (direct rotation searches) was carried out with lysozyme search molecules with different hinge bending-angles. The starting model was subjected to several rounds of CNS SA-refinement and subsequently refined with TNT. Positve density was observed around crystal contact sites. These features, presumably PEG molecules, could not be modeled unambigously and were therefore omitted from the final model.
